{"tid":1973343,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實香港人想要民主 定係要民主作工具嚟達成目標","createTime":"2020-04-15T06:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T08:23:00.000Z","uid":130406,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c9a4467e962946c51783d0b24512f47d4d8daf","tid":1973343,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:45:51.000Z","msg":"香港人要真正自治或者更遠嘅港獨<br />\n暫時可行嘅手法係達成真雙普選 即民主制度<br />\n<br />\n但如果香港實行真正民主<br />\n雖然現實上香港主流都係黃<br />\n但假設藍絲大中華係佔多數<br />\n咁連登仔少數願唔願意服從多數<br />\n融入支那 選保皇黨做特首<br />\n定係夾硬想嘗試武裝革命輸打贏要<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>民主一人一票係唔係我哋真正目標<br />\n定還是係只係想透過民主達到我哋嘅目標？</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"4e249f78c97f1ead0697f2341d1c918d8068d1a1","tid":1973343,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:51:53.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"f67ac2b2459c6834ab47abec1bbeb0dcee2fad86","tid":1973343,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T06:56:19.000Z","msg":"香港獨立"},{"pid":"3013e81f95bab46ed6ad5e5dd7924dfef96b4b1b","tid":1973343,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"如果藍絲大中華佔大多數<br />\n咁香港就一早已經融入咗支那<br />\n好似澳門咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0718c9be719c360376a6cb92812a77a6d5d396f","tid":1973343,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3013e81f95bab46ed6ad5e5dd7924dfef96b4b1b","tid":1973343,"uid":26820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:06:11.000Z","msg":"如果藍絲大中華佔大多數<br />\n咁香港就一早已經融入咗支那<br />\n好似澳門咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T07:07:03.000Z","msg":"同埋佔大多數黎講 香港又點可能有「民主」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac2d5c40f321f17e3201b1343c017eaf18779957","tid":1973343,"uid":185121,"